entries.content: When a prospect says 'I don't have any time at the moment', respond with a conditional close like 'Alright, be good time to call you back?'
entries.notes: Attempting to reschedule or gain commitment on a future time after an initial time objection.

entries.content: Recognize that 'I don't have time' is often a reflex response used by prospects to end a sales call quickly.
entries.notes: Understanding the nature of the objection helps in handling it effectively.

focus_area: Handling "Think About It": "What specifically?", Conditional closing
